d\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"employees\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The beginning of the 1980s found Olympic facing more strikes, which sought to implement regulation flights and improve economic earnings.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The beginning\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1980s\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"more strikes\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation flights\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"economic earnings\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1982, the airline celebrated twenty-five years of operation.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the airline\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"twenty-five years\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"operation\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the early 1990s, the staff had picked up Sundays, holidays, and night itineraries.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early 1990s\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"the staff\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"Sundays\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"holidays\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"night itineraries\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However on October 4th, bloody incidents unfolded between strikers and redundant and riot police outside the building of Olympic Catering.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"October 4th\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"bloody incidents\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"strikers\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Catering\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On March 28, 2001, the airline made its last flight, from the Hellinikon airport for Thessaloniki.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thessaloniki_Airport\", \"score\": 0.9999924156846857, \"rank\": 7.584334674477673e-06, \"text\": \"Thessaloniki\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thessaloniki_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thessaloniki_Airport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"the airline\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2947}, {\"ngram\": \"its last flight\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"the Hellinikon airport\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On December 31, 2009, Olympic Airlines ceased all operations, as flights toGreek islandshad already been allocated and were being flown by other carriers.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Airlines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"all operations\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"flights toGreek\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"other carriers\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flights to destinations outside of the European Union had been allocated to other carriers, which began operating them from January 1, 2010.\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3220, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999976684194, \"rank\": 